nodes.body: This does have the effect of pulling in `Logic.Equiv.Basic` into `Data.Nat.Cast.Basic`, which wasn't necessary before. If it's possible to avoid that, it would be nice, but it looks like it is not terrible, in any case.

By moving `Equiv.ofBijective` from `Logic.Equiv.Basic` to `Logic.Equiv.Defs`, I could make `Algebra.Group.TypeTags` not depend on the former. However, `Algebra.Group.Equiv.Basic` still needs quite a lot of it, so I will declare it's not my problem at this point anymore.

Pull request successfully merged into master.
